Class DefaultProxyStore

java.lang.Object
com.google.web.bindery.requestfactory.shared.DefaultProxyStore
All Implemented Interfaces:
ProxyStore
public class DefaultProxyStore extends Object implements ProxyStore
An in-memory ProxyStore store that can encode its state as a JSON object literal.
